+      analysisRecord(['h02'], `Mean PFS declined across feature_027 levels 0, 1, and 2 (${levelMeans('feature_027').map((x) => `${x.level}: ${x.mean.toFixed(3)}`).join(', ')} months); adjusted slope ${adj('feature_027').beta.toFixed(3)} months per level.`, adj('feature_027').beta, adj('feature_027').p, 'Level means and full multivariable OLS coefficient for feature_027.'));
